alertMessages.title: Let's try again
alertMessages.message:
The %d goes with the %@ symbol 
 so tap the %d

steps.text: First, look at the symbols in the key. Each symbol is paired with a number.
steps.title: Symbols

steps.text: You should tap the number that is paired with each symbol.
steps.title: Matching

steps.text:
The first four symbols are prefilled for you. 

 Match the remaining five symbols.
steps.title: Time to practice!

steps.text: Fill in the rows on the next screen the same way, by tapping the number that goes with the symbol. Work as fast as you can. Even if you make a mistake, just keep going. You will play for 90 seconds.
steps.title: Good work! Let's start.

steps.text: Good Job! You completed this activity. Tap Next to continue.
steps.title: Thank you.
